{"tid":376973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【興德之亂】陳章萍向校董會發律師信 稱若校長室物品擺錯位要負責","createTime":"2017-08-27T11:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T16:20:18.000Z","uid":8360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7db37021579628bcf427139c46ae4f0fb52e4b9","tid":376973,"uid":8360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:31:49.000Z","msg":"被揭發校內管治混亂而解僱校長的興德學校昨日舉行小一家長日，委任校董雷其昌透露因前校長陳章萍仍未交出賬簿，且聲稱忘記銀行戶口密碼，致未能以自動轉賬的方式支薪給教職員，須以支票出糧。陳章萍於8月24號透過律師向興德校董會放出律師信，指校方單方面終止（Unilateral termination) 校長一職是錯誤的決定，律師會保留一切向有關當局控訴校董會的權利。律師信中又提及校董會沒有權利單方面打開校長室，因校長室內仍有很多校長珍貴且有紀念價值的私人物品，若發現校長室內的物品有遺失、被偷、放置錯誤或損壞，校董會要負上全部責任。<br />\n<br />\n雷其昌稱，遭解僱的前校長陳章萍8月24日委託律師來學校進行接收，交收工作持續3小時，雖然校長物品交收已完成，但陳仍未交出賬簿，且仍有支援人員合約未能找到，影響學校評估是否需要招聘新的支援人員，當中包括負責照顧特殊教育需要（SEN）學生、新來港學童的職員等，陳亦稱忘記用於支薪的銀行戶口密碼，故校方需以支票出糧，「唔可以用電子轉賬去支人工畀同事，咁所以我哋一早準備咗用支票」。<br />\n興德學校今年錄取85個小一新生，當中包括28個插班生，共開4班，雷其昌指暫未有數據顯示有多少人是跨境學生，但補充今年較多本地生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170827/57133941\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170827%2F57133941&d=%2FMd9pphgY26K6J%2BQVtP%2F6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=11a0288f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170827%2F57133941&h=f47097b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170827/57133941</a><br />\n<br />\n忘記銀行戶口密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講都冇人信"},{"pid":"21fbdb7a6c1ba250fe8eec055710efbeb91fc385","tid":376973,"uid":30873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"依個咁既死肥婆，快撚啲入去坐監啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b116a6c69615b484928ba118c05b6702b64db206","tid":376973,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:39:14.000Z","msg":"條友個名而家o係全港都臭曬<br />\n<br />\n佢愈係玩野, 全港人愈係見到佢就屌<br />\n<br />\n睇黎佢真係enjoy做香港公敵"},{"pid":"61713153ef476e8a17a012496e7661b30ba1065d","tid":376973,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"俾人炒咗仲可以咁惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3f7367c60193225f31933b79eb344fdefbace8","tid":376973,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"唔好攞我啲餅卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2c3c9cf5a45a85eda99a2fdd94dbb74d407e03","tid":376973,"uid":136773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"如~ 肥婆全沒了 銀行全沒了<br />\n誰人讓我保駕"},{"pid":"af8338dd2b1d06cd9ef2bd3235d02fda81bb5563","tid":376973,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如~ 肥婆全沒了 銀行全沒了<br />\n誰人讓我保駕</blockquote><br />\n肥婆會唔會建國，組織肥婆軍？"},{"pid":"19c78796b64b089cdfeae78587af8dfe5a703b1c","tid":376973,"uid":8360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:06:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好攞我啲餅卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7527b87621d91217c9fc9ccb04f22339f503a3","tid":376973,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:07:11.000Z","msg":"一樣咁仆街<br />\n奇華不如搵肥校長做代言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2ef1ca1f1a4d58b352f7c76ae4ea4a07ec5680","tid":376973,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:07:42.000Z","msg":"等睇ICAC 拉尻個肥婆"},{"pid":"137b52b046b6c0aa7ea84e849c302d68e4bf099d","tid":376973,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"無數簿有無機會係虧空左公款呢?"},{"pid":"698b84a08a62d99ad1ca2a6adb026244207c08a8","tid":376973,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017